node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dustin Connell on August 05, 2021. May be an image of body of water.

node.text:
Not competing today at Lake Champlain in the Bass Pro Tour. Never expected to be in this position, but life takes turns when you least expect it..

Update: I came down with COVID and was admitted to the hospital for 4 days with double Pneumonia. I’ve now been released and at the house healing up..It’s been a scary/life changing event, but I’m THANKFUL that the Lord above has allowed me to continue to heal and get better. It’s just going to take time. Thank you ALL for the thoughts and prayers along the way and please continue to pray for a speedy recovery for anyone right now that is in need 🙏
